Name: Aster
Notes: Primary cosmic goddess, protector of her children below, creator of the Milky Way through stirring cosmic milk

Name: Andromeda
Notes: Companion goddess whose love shines from afar, bound to Aster by Lambda force

Name: Lambda
Notes: Cosmic force that binds Aster and Andromeda together like a star

Name: Juno
Notes: Goddess who guides Steppenwolves and gas giants, cosmic guide wandering through the night

Name: Brunhilda
Notes: Guardian goddess of failed stars and brown dwarfs, watches over stars with incomplete fusion

Name: Ruby
Notes: Red dwarf star goddess, small but ever bright, witness to cosmic dusk and the Omega Point

Name: Chrystella
Notes: Main sequence star goddess with vibrant youthful glow, becomes white dwarf in old age

Name: Celestella
Notes: Red supergiant goddess commanding giant blazes, watches supernovae and neutron stars

Name: Gigastella
Notes: Massive star goddess, sister to Celestella, collapsed into supernova and then black hole

Name: Steppenwolves
Notes: Cosmic entities guided by Juno, associated with gas giants
